    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Manifest of projects for CART Modules – Hydra and Cerberus, Cn Conv modules",
        "CN Conv PF team shall give revision number of all CART and CN Conv PF modules in their release notes for each release",
        "Project Manifest shall point CART & CN Conv PF modules to the revision mentioned in the release notes"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "CN Conv PF team shall give revision number of all CART and CN Conv Config repos"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Manifest of Project for Config modules"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Options:"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": true,
      "items": [
        "It will be good if we have config repos for each project",
        "Another approach is to create branch for each project",
        "Another option is to have different project folders inside the config folders -> But when we download one project repo, then it will have project folders inside config folders which is not good"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Decision:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We will create one config repos for project and for next project we will create branch out of each config repos"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Application repo:"
    },
